nuous work in Chicagoland theatre. The next Jeff Equity Awards will be held on Monday, October 13, 2014, at Drury Lane Oakbrook. _____________________________________________________________________ Non-Equity Jeff Awards to be Presented June 2: The Jeff Awards established the Non-Equity Wing in 1973 to celebrate outstanding achievement in non-union theatre. The next Non-Equity awards ceremony will be held on Monday, June 2, 2014, at Park West. Join us on Now Playing Equity Wing | see complete list Cock Buzzer Russian Transport Gypsy Chicago's Golden Soul Non-Equity Wing | see complete list Return of Neverland Happy Amadeus Into the Woods The Playboy of the Western World NEWS Special Award for Dale Benson TCG Looks at Theatre Awards 2013 Non-Equity Jeff Award Recipients Jeff Recommended indicates that at least one element of a show was deemed excellent by opening night judges. The entire production is then eligible for nomination for awards at the end of the season. SUPPORT THE JEFF AWARDS 2014 The Joseph Jefferson Awards. All Rights Reserved. The Internet Off-Broadway Database Search for: Category: All Theatre People Awards 2011 The Lucille Lortel Awards. 2014 Lucille Lortel Awards 29th Annual Lucille Lortel Awards Recipients Announced to be Hosted by Megan Mullally and Nick Offerman. Producer Robyn Goodman to be Honored with the Lifetime Achievement Award. Click for More. The Actors Fund is a beneficiary of the 2014 Lortel Awards 322 Eighth Avenue, 21st Floor New York, NY 10001 Tel (212) 924-2817 Fax (212) 989-0036 Home | Nominees and Recipients | Recent News | Photo Gallery | Program The 12 th San Diego : Outstanding Resident Musical Outstanding New Musical Outstanding Musical Direction Outstanding Choreography Outstanding Orchestrations Outstanding Ensemble Outstanding Solo Performance Outstanding Lead Performance in a Musical, Female Outstanding Lead Performance in a Musical, Male Outstanding Featured Performance in a Musical, Male Outstanding Featured Performa